description: Possible sizes of the torsion group of an elliptic curve over some quadratic extension of the rationals Q. This is the full sequence.
references: Kamienny, S. Torsion points on elliptic curves and q-coefficients of modular forms. Invent. Math. 109, No. 2, 221-229 (1992).
Kenku, M.A.; Momose, F. Torsion points on elliptic curves defined over quadratic fields. Nagoya Math. J. 109, 125-149 (1988).
author: Noam Katz (noamkj(AT)hotmail.com), Mar 30 2001
